caller_intent: Matthew, owner of D L G Hard Skate LLC, sought a general liability insurance quote for his newly formed retaining wall construction business, which he has not yet insured.
resolution_steps: Anna confirmed the company name (D L G Hard Skate LLC) and clarified the type of insurance requested (general liability).
Anna explained that producers would contact Matthew to discuss details and generate quotes.
Matthew agreed to a producer callback, specifying availability for the next day.
knowledge_required: Understanding business insurance types (general liability for construction services)
Onboarding process for new business clients
summary: Matthew, owner of a new retaining wall construction company, requested general liability insurance through Alliance Insurance. Anna confirmed details and scheduled a producer callback for the next day. The call established a lead for business insurance.
